{
  "stem": "1496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The blood was pouring, so they had a couple of pails of water, and they were pouring water onto people, in order to keep them alive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All kind of things, you cannot describe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even Spielberg show you in the movie where Goeth used to stay on his balcony and shoot people right from the balcony.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the-- the worst camp I can imagine, because the harassment and the beating.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every day, there were a few people missing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we came to the barracks, we were always looking around, who is missing because he was shot during the day?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, while I was working over there in this machine shop, one day a Jewish policeman, kapo, came to the shop and called my name and ordered me to go to my barrack, take any belongings I have, and report on the police station.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was really concerned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was afraid, because that's the way selections were made.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were round up from various shops and they were taken to a spot and executed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't want to tell me what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had to follow the orders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I came to the police station with few belongings, what I had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Over there, there were about 40 men assembled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After a while, a truck pulls over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They loaded us on a truck and they sent us away from this camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The ride was very short, because only about 10 miles away from this camp was Schindler's factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was my lucky day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's the day I was sent to Schindler's factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The barracks were-- were big, wooden barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the barracks, the only thing you had along the walls-- and you saw them-- you saw those in many movies-- there were bunkbeds, three tiers bunks.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
